item.title: Supruga (Супруга) 3x
item.description: No one is safe After Хаос (chaos, 2019), the most recent album (an EP) is Никто не в безопасности (no one is safe, 2020). Only three tracks, with this as the final and title track. You can also listen on Spotify and Bandcamp , where the lyrics are also available for those who look closely.
